Insider Activity


Individual




Robert Patrick Myron



Mr. Robert P. Myron, CPA, is on the Board of Directors at James River Group Holdings Ltd. Mr. Myron was previously employed as Head-Investor Relations by The Hanover Insurance Group, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer by PXRE Reinsurance Co., President by Select Reinsurance Ltd., Chief Financial Officer by Argo Group International Holdings Ltd., and Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer by PXRE Group Ltd. He received his undergraduate degree from Babson College.



