Pens, Pencils & Highlighters

Multifunction Pens

Light Pens






				Flashlight Pens



Promote your company name on flashlight pens from Myron and be seen everywhere. Featuring powerful LED lights, our selection offers a wide variety of materials, colors and prices to beat your budget and your advertising goals. Design your own custom flashlight pens below and don’t miss our novelty pens and custom gel pens, too! 
Shine Attention on Your Brand with Custom Flashlight Pens
Choose your favorite flashlight pen below, then upload your artwork with Myron’s intuitive personalization tool (on select products), or e-mail your logo to our designers and let us handle the rest. If you need a logo or graphic, our artists are ready to help. Did you know impressions from pens easily make them the best value of any promotional item? With Myron’s 100% satisfaction guarantee, flashlight pens are a smart marketing and budget decision. 
Pens are practical, highly visible and often change hands over the course of their usable life. That’s an incredible return on investment, and a great way to reflect the professionalism and style of your brand. Myron’s flashlight pens, custom stylus pens, personalized stick pens, and other pens, pencils and highlighters make desired giveaways at every event. Shop today and design a flashlight pen to promote your company.

